  <description>
    <p>
      Behold the ultimate GNOME Tool for creating memes on the go.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Add top and bottom text to any image</li>
      <li>Classic meme styling with Impact font</li>
      <li>Real-time preview as you type</li>
      <li>Export memes as PNG images</li>
      <li>Dark mode support</li>
      <li>Let it Happen</li>

    </ul>
